      <h1 class="mb-4">School Management API Project Educase India</h1>

      <h2>Project Overview</h2>
      <p>
        APIs developed using Node.js, Express.js, and MySQL to manage school
        data, including adding new schools and retrieving them based on
        proximity to a specified location.
      </p>

      <h2>Implemented APIs</h2>
      <h3>1. Add School API</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Endpoint:</strong>
        <code>https://educase-india-assignment-kappa.vercel.app/addSchool</code>
      </p>
      <p><strong>Method:</strong> POST</p>
      <p>Adds a new school after validating the input data.</p>

      <h3>2. List Schools API</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Endpoint:</strong>
        <code
          >https://educase-india-assignment-kappa.vercel.app/listSchools</code
        >
      </p>
      <p><strong>Method:</strong> GET</p>
      <p>Retrieves and sorts schools based on proximity to user's location.</p>

      <h2>Additional Routes</h2>
      <h3>1. Delete All Schools API</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Endpoint:</strong>
        <code
          >https://educase-india-assignment-kappa.vercel.app/deleteAllSchools</code
        >
      </p>
      <p><strong>Method:</strong> DELETE</p>
      <p>Deletes all schools from the database.</p>

      <h3>2. Delete School by ID API</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Endpoint:</strong>
        <code
          >https://educase-india-assignment-kappa.vercel.app/deleteSchool</code
        >
      </p>
      <p><strong>Method:</strong> DELETE</p>
      <p>Deletes a school based on the provided ID.</p>

